{ 14.Ba3  is more human. } 14... Bh3 15. N1d2 O-O-O 16. Qc2 Bxf1 17. O-O-O Qh6
18. Rxf1 b6
{ The previous sequence was pretty forced. Believe it or not, computers assess this complicated position as equal. }
