5... e5
{ White needs to be careful here. The alternative  5...d5  6.e5  Nd7  complicates matters. }
6. O-O g5 { Computers like this direct attack. } 7. Be2 g4 8. hxg4 Bxg4 9. d4
Rg8 10. d5 Ne7
{ With a very unclear position where White can get under attack. } *

