{ This is a better setup for the c3-d4 plan.  6.Re1  Nc6  7.c3  e6  8.d4  cxd4  9.cxd4  d5  10.e5  Ne4=  Compared to the  @@StartFEN@@rn1qkbnr/pp1Bpppp/3p4/2p5/4P3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQK2R b KQkq - 0 4@@EndFEN@@  4...Nxd7  line, Black has no problems here. }
6... Nc6 7. c3 e6 8. d4 cxd4 9. cxd4 d5 10. e5 Ne4
