6... O-O { 6...Qb6  has to be checked, it may be enough to equalize. } 7. h3
{ Is too slow. } 7... e5
{ Should equalize. Also  7...Qb6  8.a4  d6  looks fine for Black. While @@StartFEN@@r1bq1rk1/pp1pppbp/2n2np1/1Bp5/4P3/2P2N1P/PP1P1PP1/RNBQR1K1 b - - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7...d6  doesn't work as White plays  8.d4  right away. }
8. d4 cxd4 9. cxd4 Nxd4
{ 9...d5  10.dxe5  Nxe4  11.Nc3  Be6  may be enough for Black to equalize the game. }
10. Nxd4 Qb6
{ Computers' recommendation. Also good is  10...exd4  11.Qxd4  a6  12.Ba4   11...d5  12.e5  Ne4  13.Nc3  Nxc3  14.bxc3 }
