7. Bf4 O-O 8. Bc7 Qe7 9. Bd6 Bxd6 10. Qxd6 Qd8 11. O-O-O a6 12. Nd4 Ne7
{ White has a significant lead in development, but Black has his play with ...b5 and ...Bb7. }
