{ 9.Be3  Be7  10.f4  O-O  11.Nb3  b5  and @@StartFEN@@r1b1kb1r/1pq2ppp/p1nppn2/8/3NP3/2N3P1/PPP2PBP/R1BQ1RK1 w kq - 0 9@@EndFEN@@  9.Nxc6!?  bxc6  10.Na4  Be7  are standard Sicilians. }
