{ This move allows Black to stay away from the main lines. Unfortunately, it's too passive. }
9. Nxc6
{ I find this recent discovery quite unpleasant, and it's the reason why I would recommend Black players not to play this line. }
9... bxc6 { The critical move. White has two challenging replies. } 10. Qd4 Be7
{ Or  10...Bd6  11.f4  e5  12.Qd2  . } 11. e5 Nd5 12. Nxd5 cxd5 13. c4
{ White has a very powerful initiative. } *

