10. Ne2 Qxe4 11. Rg1 Qc4
{ Risky, but Black is a pawn above and White has to prove he has enough compensation. In the game Karjakin-Rapport, Stavanger 2021, Rapport very quickly got to a winning position. Then White managed to defend himself and the game ended in a draw, but White was much better very soon. }
