{ 9...Na5  was tried by Matlakov against Carlsen in Wijk aan Zee 2018.  10.a3  Bxc3  11.Qxc3  Qxc3+  12.bxc3  d5  13.exd5  exd5  14.Nb3  Nc4  15.Bd4  Ne4  and White has a slightly better endgame, very close to a draw @@StartBracket@@even if Magnus managed to win it@@EndBracket@@.   9...Ng4  should be checked, there are almost no games in this line.  10.Bg1  O-O  11.e5 }
