7... Ne5
{ Interesting but extremely risky, it has been played several times by Anish Giri in 2014/ 2015. }
8. Qg3 h5
{ It seems contrary to every chess principle, but the engines - without which probably no one would have even considered it - support it.   8...b5  9.O-O-O  Nf6  transposes to the main line. }
9. f4 { Also  9.Bf4  d6  10.Bg5  can be tried. } 9... h4 10. Qh3 Nc4
