O-O-O b5
{ Black has no development and his position looks awful. But it has some potential, and White must be very accurate. }
13. f5
{ Also  13.Kb1  Bb7  14.Rhe1  , as played by Leko in 2019 against Shankland, is good for White. }
13... Bb7 14. Kb1 Nf6 15. Rhe1
{ An extremely sharp and complicated position that needs to be thoroughly analyzed, but it is favorable for White. }
