9... Nbxd5 10. Nxd5 Qxd5 11. Nb5 { The only try for White. } 11... O-O 12. Nc3
Qh5 { An important move to match White's queen activity. } 13. Be2 Qg6
{ Black is very active - there's simply nothing which White can justifiably claim for an edge. }
