{ In this lesson we will introduce the Sveshnikov and White's alternatives to the main line 7. Bg5. According to current theory, it is very difficult for White to prove an advantage against the Sveshnikov. It is successfully employed by numerous grandmasters - I have played it throughout my career and it is one of the main weapons of world champion Magnus Carlsen, who prepared it for his 2018 match with Fabiano Caruana - and it is one of the most popular Sicilians at any level.   After all, it is not so often that Black can play with the initiative right from the opening! }
