16. h5
{ Maybe this is more accurate than starting with Bh3, although I don't think that will change much in the evaluation of the position. White needs to be careful, this h-pawn march might fire back, castling now will always be in Black's favor. If not then the king will always be in danger. }
16... Bg5 17. Qf3 Rc8
{ Even if the position is equal according to the machines, I will always take Black in this position in a practical game. }
