{ And here during the 1990s I had a lot of games in this position, it wasn't easy at the time but nowadays it is clear that Black is more or less fine in this position. }
16. Qh5 e4 17. Bc2 Ne7
{ I played two or three games here with Black and there were small issues here and there but with the help of modern engines I can be sure that this is safe for Black. }
18. Nf4 { I remember that this was one of the moves I used to face. } 18... Qd7
{ I remember that I even played this move once. } 19. Nxe6 Qxe6 20. Bb3 d5
{ Strangely enough White can't make use of this diagonal. Rd8 is coming. } *

