{ Many computer games have been played from this position and even they have problems holding with Black. That could mean that the position is really dangerous for Black. For instance, one of the possible main lines could follow  16...Kh7  17.Bxg7  Kxg7  18.fxg4  Bxg4  19.Nf5+  Bxf5  20.exf5  Rh8  21.fxg6  Nxg6  22.Qd5  and White is attacking. }
*

