Nexg4
{ Dangerous, but it is Black's best move.  12...Bc6  13.f3  followed by g5 is in White's favor. }
13. Bxg4 Nxg4 14. Rhg1 e5 15. Nd5 Qd8 16. Nxe7+ Qxe7 17. Bg3 f6
