e5 { The light-squared bishop is hanging, and Black's play is forced. } 15...
dxe5 16. fxe5 Nd5 { A series of forced exchanges now follows. } 17. Nxd5 exd5
18. Qxd5 Qxd5 19. Rxd5 Bc6 20. Rd2
