13. Qxa1 d5 { An important move. } 14. exd5 Bxb4
{ The position has simplified enormously and is heading to a draw. In conclusion, @@StartFEN@@r1bqkb1r/pp3ppp/2nppn2/6B1/3NP3/2N5/PPP2PPP/R2QKB1R w KQkq - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7.Qd3  Bd7  solves Black's problems. However, White players can try this system to surprise their opponents, especially those who reply to  @@StartFEN@@r1bqkb1r/pp3ppp/2nppn2/6B1/3NP3/2N5/PPP2PPP/R2QKB1R w KQkq - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7.Qd2  with  7...a6  . }
