{ Same as @@StartFEN@@r1bqk2r/pp2bppp/2nppn2/6B1/3NP3/2N5/PPPQ1PPP/2KR1B1R b kq - 3 8@@EndFEN@@  8...O-O  9.h4  Nxd4  . We don't care what our opponent does and go with our idea.   Of course,  10.f3  or  10.f4  are possible, but I recommend this idea. }
