1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6 6. Qe2 e5
{ This move could be considered as the refutation of 6.Qe2.   6...g6  7.Bg5  Bg7  8.O-O-O  is playable for White. }
7. Nb3 Be6 8. Be3 Nbd7 9. O-O-O Rc8 { ...Rxc8 is a problem. } 10. Qd2
