6... e6 7. a4 { 7.Be2  b5  is good for Black. } 7... Bd7
{ After  7...Nc6  8.Nxc6  bxc6  9.Qg3  , White got his queen to g3 but a4 hasn't been a useful move. Carlsen has beaten Grandelius from this position in Wijk aan Zee in 2021, but judging by the game, it probably had little to do with the outcome of the opening:    9...Bb7  10.Be2  Be7  11.Bf4  e5  12.Be3  O-O  13.O-O  Kh8  14.a5  Nd7  15.Rfd1  f5  16.exf5  d5  17.Na4  d4  18.Bd2  c5  19.Qh3  Bg5  20.Bxg5  Qxg5  21.Re1  Be4  22.Bd3  Bxf5  23.Bxf5  Rxf5  24.Nb6  Nxb6  25.axb6  h6  26.Qd3  Rb8  27.Rxa6  Rf6  28.g3  Rfxb6  29.Rxb6  Rxb6  30.f4  Qd8  31.Rxe5  Rxb2  32.Rxc5  Qa8  33.Kf2  Rb8  34.Qf3  Qa7  35.Qd5  Qa1  36.Qe5  Qb2  37.Rc6  Kh7  38.Rc7  Rg8  39.Kg2  Qb4  40.Qe4+  Kh8  41.Rd7  Qd2+  42.Kh3  Qd1  43.Re7  Qh5+  44.Kg2  Rc8  45.f5  Qd1  46.Re8+  Rxe8  47.Qxe8+  Kh7  48.Qe4  Kh8  49.Qe8+  Kh7  50.Qg6+  Kh8  51.f6  Qe2+  52.Kh3  Qe6+  53.Kh4  gxf6  54.Qxh6+  Kg8  55.Qg6+  Kf8  56.g4  Qe5  57.h3  Ke7  58.Qf5  Qe3  59.Kh5  Qxh3+  60.Kg6  Kd6  61.Kxf6  Qe3  62.g5  Qe7+  63.Kg6  Qe8+  64.Kg7  Qe7+  65.Kg8  1-0, Carlsen @@StartBracket@@2862@@EndBracket@@ - Grandelius @@StartBracket@@2663@@EndBracket@@, Wijk aan Zee 2021. }
8. a5 Be7 9. Be2 Nc6 10. Nxc6 Bxc6 11. O-O O-O 12. Be3 Nd7
{ After 6.Qd3, White can't get more than this position. It's not a forced draw but clearly, Black has a good Scheveningen position. }
