11. Nd2 { Allows Black the ...b5 break. } 11... b5 12. Nf1
{ Continuing the route to e3. } 12... b4
{ Comes just in time when the knights aren't coordinating. } 13. Nd5 Bxd5 14.
exd5 a5 { It's not clear what the knight is doing on f1. } *

