{ The standard and logical choice, and also what most players are playing now. }
11... Be7 { Defending. } 12. Nd5 Bxd5 { We take the knight, as always. } 13.
Qxd5 Nd7 14. Kb1
{ White has dreams of maneuvering the knight to d5 one day, but it simply takes too long. }
14... O-O 15. Qd3 { Necessary sooner or later. } 15... b5
{ h4 is necessary to prevent ...Bg5 and exchanging the bishop on the knight's path. You get the picture that it takes too long to prepare such an idea and Black in the meantime can create dangerous queenside counterplay. }
