8. Be3
{ Most of the time this leads to a transposition, but there is some independent value. }
8... Be6 9. f4 { This is too hasty. } 9... exf4
{ Winning a tempo on the bishop. } 10. Bxf4 Nc6 11. Qd2 d5
{ Many games have been fought here, but it's an equal position after Black gets in this freeing break. }
