7... Nc6
{ Must be played to hit at the center, as this a4 move makes it inconvenient to continue queenside play.  7...b6  is not playable on account of  8.Bf3  Ra7  due to the threat of e5  9.Be3   or it's the same story after  7...Be7  8.Be3  O-O  9.O-O  when you can't really delay ...Nc6 any longer as after  9...b6   9...Qc7  10.a5  Nc6  11.Nb3  is also unpleasant for Black due to the weak b6 square.  10.Bf3  Ra7  11.a5  is a problem. }
