8... exf4 9. Bxf4 Nc6 10. Qe2
{ After  10.Qd2  , Black equalizes easily with  10...d5  . } 10... Rc8
{ Since White's next move is going to be h3 as, otherwise, long castle would run into ... Bg4, you can also play  10...Be7  and after  11.h3  , we have a transposition to  the h3 line. Nevertheless, you don't even need to bother about that, as the text move is a very strong one. }
