{ The game Leko-Giri continued  13...e5  14.Bh2  dxe4  15.g5  hxg5  16.hxg5  Rxh2  @@StartBracket@@Black is playing only moves@@EndBracket@@  17.Rxh2  exd4  18.Rh4  and now the amazing  18...Ng4!  19.Rxg4  Nc5  20.Rh4  d3  21.Nd4  Bb7  and this incredible mess finally ended in a draw. Maybe Black holds, but that means walking on thin ice. }
