{ The most dangerous move at top level.  10...Nbd7  11.c4  and White is already better. }
9... Bxd5 10. exd5 Nbd7 11. Qd2 g6
{ The idea of playing 8...h5 before commiting the dark-squared bishop, which is better placed on g7 than on e7. }
