{ I'm not quite sure that this move equalizes, but maybe it's close. I've analyzed some positions in this system and I couldn't find anything special with White more than a tiny plus. }
13. Qa5 Bh6 14. Bxh6 Rxh6
{ The trade of the dark-squared bishops helps Black. } 15. Qd2 Rh8 16. f4 Nbd7
{ The position is still very complicated, but Black is fine. } *

