Qd7 16. Nxe7+ Qxe7 17. Bxb6 Nxb6 18. Qxd6 { White gets the pawn back. } 18...
Qg5+ 19. Qd2 Qf6
{ The position is completely equal and should end in a draw without turbulences. }
