{ We've seen how important it is to have some general knowledge and a feeling for transpositions. You can easily get better positions with White or Black thanks to your better understanding of the opening as a whole.Very often, players don't pay attention to these details, but they can be decisive for the outcome of the opening, and the game.In this course, I'll explain to you plans, ideas and details about the different Sicilian systems, together with an update on the state of theory. }
